Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_report...strained_paths(25.10)    timing_report...strained_paths(25.10)

Name
       timing_report_enable_clock_to_for_unconstrained_paths

Syntax
       timing_report_enable_clock_to_for_unconstrained_paths

       {true | false}

       Default : false

       Enables  unconstrained  path reporting when the report_timing -to_clock
       parameter is specified.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

